import React from "react"
import { Box, Text,Heading ,Stack} from "@chakra-ui/layout"
import { Radio, RadioGroup } from "@chakra-ui/react"

export const UserPreferences=()=>{
    const [value, setValue] = React.useState("1")
    return(
        <>
        
        <Box alignItems="center" padding="50">
        <Box maxW="60%" borderWidth="1px" borderRadius="lg" overflow="hidden" m="auto" padding="25">

                <Heading>1.Climate Condition would you expect while travelling?</Heading>

                <RadioGroup onChange={setValue} value={value}>
                <Stack direction="column" >
                    <Radio value="1">First</Radio>
                    <Radio value="2">Second</Radio>
                    <Radio value="3">Third</Radio>
                </Stack>
                </RadioGroup>

        </Box>
        </Box>
        
        
        </>
    )
}
